race.comment: MAJESTIC FRED (4) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing third (17.78) at this track over 300m. One of the leading chances. THAT'S OKAY (7) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing third (17.72) and beaten 6 lengths over 300m at this track. Can feature again. SNACKS (1) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (17.83) at this track. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. TIGRESS WINK (2) is a chance after winning last time.
